                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "s8zF9C",
                      "name": "正文列",
                      "width": 760,
                      "height": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 20,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "xdTBk",
                          "name": "段落1",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "雨从傍晚开始就没停过。码头的灯在水汽里发黄，把整条栈桥映成一条湿亮的线。林舟把斗篷领口拉紧，仍能感到冷风从缝隙里钻进来，带着铁锈、海藻和一点烧焦木头的味道。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.78,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "O2gb9",
                          "name": "段落2",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "「他真会来？」身后的少年压低声音问。声音很轻，却还是在空旷的雨声里显得突兀。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.78,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "Gn97I",
                          "name": "段落3",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "林舟没有立刻回答。他望着港口尽头那盏忽明忽暗的航标灯，像是在等某个只有他自己才懂的信号。三天前，那封没有落款的信只写了一句话：雨夜，三号仓，带上旧地图。",
                          "lineHeight": 1.78,
                          "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                          "fontSize": 18,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "u4RWh4",
