                                  "fill": "$text-primary",
                                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                  "width": "fill_container",
                                  "content": "「会。」林舟终于开口。他从怀里取出那张被反复折叠的羊皮纸，指尖在边缘停顿了一下，「如果他还记得十年前的约定。」",
                                  "lineHeight": 1.78,
                                  "fontFamily": "$font-body",
                                  "fontSize": 18,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                }
                              ]
                            }
